title: SAMSUNG Galaxy Z Fold6 Crafted Black, 256GB, Factory Unlocked
description: The Samsung Galaxy Z Fold6 Crafted Black is a factory-unlocked, foldable smartphone with a sleek, durable design featuring a 6.3-inch cover display and a 7.6-inch main Dynamic AMOLED 2X screen, both with a 120Hz refresh rate. Powered by a Snapdragon 8 Gen 3 processor, 12GB RAM, and 256GB storage, it ensures high performance. Its triple rear camera system includes a 50MP wide, 12MP ultra-wide, and 10MP telephoto lens, alongside a 10MP cover and 4MP under-display front cameras. A 4,400mAh battery supports fast wired, wireless, and reverse wireless charging. With 5G connectivity, S Pen support, and an IP48 rating for durability, it offers a premium multitasking experience.
